            <h3>Getting Started</h3>
            <p>To access our services, contact our intake department to schedule an initial assessment. During this process, we will:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Review your needs and goals</li>
                <li>Determine eligibility for services</li>
                <li>Develop an individualized service plan</li>
                <li>Connect you with appropriate programs and supports</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>Funding Sources</h3>
            <p>We work with various funding sources to make our services accessible, including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Medicaid waiver programs</li>
                <li>Department of Developmental Disabilities (DDD)</li>
                <li>Private insurance</li>
                <li>Private pay</li>
                <li>Grants and donations</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>Service Areas</h3>
